# Skeleton Extraction from Images using OpenCV

## ğŸ“Œ Overview
Skeleton extraction (also called morphological thinning) reduces objects in an image to thin representations preserving the basic structure and connectivity.

This project uses *Python + OpenCV* to extract skeletons from images using morphological operations.

